(31772, 'Rogue Stache', 2017, 'Rogue Stache is an action-adventure platforming roguelike which draws heavy inspiration from hits such as Rogue Legacy, Risk of Rain, and Magicite. Explore vast interstellar dungeons and defeat hordes of cunning enemies!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/nhifmgqu5hfagllugal9.jpg', null),

