(31598, 'Redout: Enhanced Edition', 2016, 'Redout is a tribute to the old racing monsters such as F-Zero, WipeOut, Rollcage, and POD. It is designed to be an uncompromising, fast, tough and satisfying driving experience, soaked in that vertigo that stands at the core of the arcade racing genre.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co258s.jpg', null),

(31587, 'Tavernier', 2016, 'Tavernier is a mix between a tavern-management game and an interactive fiction. You`ll play as a barkeeper managing his tavern, coping with events, good and bad alike, in a (not so peaceful) town. A town that keeps a dark secret...', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co225p.jpg', null),

