(32455, 'L U N E', 2016, 'LUNE is a experiential haiku, a short poem dedicated to the exploration of the new medium of VR. You can touch and play; poke and prod; dance, move, caress, or simply meditate as you build yourself a pillow fort made from stars, in the company of the quiet moon.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/omzxoh8snokejg2psykk.jpg', null),

(32106, 'Ascension VR', 2016, 'Now updated with the War of Shadows expansion and support for motion controls! Come try out the expansion with the devs, Tuesday nights at 8pm Pacific. 
 
