(32241, 'Zone of Lacryma', 2016, 'Zone of Lacryma is a story driven 2D shooter inspired by the classic shmups but with a couple of twists. Custom built levels, multiple weapons, an upgrade system and a rich story to lead you through the missions.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2d9q.jpg', null),

