(32285, 'Twisted Arrow', 2017, 'Twisted Arrow is a first-person shooter that gives players adrenaline-packed arcade style action. Armed with a top secret combat bow and an arsenal of devastating arrows, you must traverse and fight your way through a city occupied by a high-tech army, mechs, zombies, and chemical monsters.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co27up.jpg', null),

