(32682, 'Monsters` Den: Godfall', 2017, 'The popular dungeon-crawling RPG series returns! Take your party into procedurally-generated dungeons, fight in turn-based battles, loot and level up! Explore the land and uncover the mysteries of the Godfall!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1wb2.jpg', null),

