(33631, 'Arena 3D', 2018, 'Fast paced, bright and colourful arcade action. Bringing you modern renditions of arcade classics such as Wipeout, Descent, Geometry Wars and many more...', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co298a.jpg', 13667),

(33601, 'Space Pilgrim Episode III: Delta Pavonis', 2016, 'Still reeling from the life-changing events of the previous episode, Gail seeks out a safe haven with her father in the Delta Pavonis system. 
However, she soon learns that the politics of Planet Leto can be as treacherous and unpredictable as the local weather. What`s more, her father seems to have disappeared under suspicious circumstances ... can she find him before her enemies catch up with her?', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1qbr.jpg', null),

(33642, 'Melon Simulator', 2016, 'Melon Simulator™ is a chaotic, multiplayer, first person melee combat game.  Almost anything that isn`t nailed down can be used to whack, slice, and throw at the oncoming melon hoard...', null, null),

(33615, 'VRChat', 2017, 'Join our growing community as you explore, play, and help craft the future of social VR. Create worlds and custom avatars. Welcome to VRChat.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co20uh.jpg', 21425),

(33849, 'Space Pilgrim Episode I: Alpha Centauri', 2015, 'Captain Gail Pilgrim has been flying starships since she was a kid, ferrying passengers between planets and space stations across the galaxy. She has no reason to expect that this latest trip to Alpha Centauri will be anything special, even if her passengers are a little more diverse than usual....', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1m9i.jpg', null),

(33710, 'Campus Notes - Forget Me Not.', 2016, 'A novel game set in the University of Tsukuba. Play as Yuta Kiriha and join the group "Bertha`s Knights" to solve a mysterious case of being forgotten every day.', null, null),

(33609, 'PIXELMAN', 2016, 'PIXELMAN is a retro styled, action-filled, endless-flyer, high-score chaser, where you control the title character in his mission to rescue the citizens of Pixville from the evil Baron Von Pixel and his contraptions.

The citizens of Pixville are counting on you!', null, null),

(33511, 'Artificial Defense', 2016, 'Artificial Defense is a one man made, real time strategy game combining orbital shooter and tower defense components within an electrifying, virtual reality setting. You are the machine, a mighty computer-system defending its servers against swarms of intruding creeps.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/vmi00nitud0l50wvtk7k.jpg', null),

(33649, 'Quar: Battle for Gate 18', 2016, 'Quar: Battle for Gate 18 is a turn-based strategic VR game set in the grimsical world of Alwyd. The Quar are cute alien ant-eaters. Don`t mistake cute for gentle. They use their WW1 level technology to wage war across the face of their world.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/spaczmvyeriapr2yaslb.jpg', null),

(33847, 'Lupinball', 2017, 'Werewolves shooting fireballs at each other! Survive each round as it becomes more and more chaotic from everyone`s fireballs bouncing around non-stop. Be the last wolf standing in this hilarious 2-4 player arcade deathmatch, local or online!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/haibdmxlmxy1gwabbjo3.jpg', null),

(33893, 'Narcissu 10th Anniversary Anthology Project', 2016, '"Life is like a waiting room, except people don`t leave in the order they enter." 
 
Narcissu is a thought provoking visual novel series about terminal illness, living, dying, and the relationship between those leaving and those left behind. There are no miracles, no heroes, no villains in this story. Just life and the characters finding their own ways of facing death in an indifferent, relentless, ever-impartial reality.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1qpq.jpg', null),

(34200, 'Voidspire Tactics', 2015, 'An indie turn-based Tactics RPG with a heavy emphasis on exploration, character progression, and highly tactical combat. Create your own deeply customizable party of Warriors, Sorcerers, and Shiftcloaks to take on the Spire!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/rncpz9lcmdfi8uv1mlji.jpg', null),

(34483, 'Bleeding Blocks', 2015, 'Bleeding Blocks is a 2D arena shooter. Two players face off in a single-screen deathmatch. Winning requires more than quick reflexes. Players must use cover and tactics to outsmart the enemy.', null, null),

(34197, 'HordeZ', 2016, 'If you are looking for a on-rails arcade experience that blends between classics like Doom, Left 4 dead and House of the Dead then we got you covered! Fast and simple gameplay that will bring you into a creepy world of zombies and demons. Show your skills to the world through our global leadboard system! Bring a friend in multiplayer Co-Op game and send those zombies flying back to hell!', null, null),

(34176, 'Midsummer Night', 2016, 'Waking up after a nap one warm July afternoon, Klim finds out that his sister Alionushka has left the house earlier. He goes looking for her, with an aim to visit the great festival of Midsummer together later that day. However, an unlikely event changes everything...', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2afv.jpg', null),

(34266, 'Roads of Rome', 2015, 'Advance into the unknown territories full of secrets and dangers. Expand the famous road system to the far corners of mighty Roman  
Empire in this blend of casual strategy, sim and time management genres!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co225d.jpg', null),

(34246, 'Space Impossible', 2016, 'Take control of a fully destructible spaceship and explore, blast or trade your way through the cosmos, alone or with friends. Every tile matters, as you dogfight, maneuver or speed your way past friendly traders, hostile aliens, and impressive space navies. What will you do, Captain?', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/bg6ownuhspbokamvpmxb.jpg', null),

(34177, 'City of Chains', 2015, 'City of Chains is a dark sci-fi RPG set in a dystopian city. Take control of a small group of escaped fugitives and lead them to their freedom. Decide whether to fight head on or to avoid combat, to help others or to go your own way, to show mercy or to kill. Your actions could affect the fate of the city.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1o8x.jpg', null),

(34191, 'Brick Inventions', 2016, 'Brick Inventions is a physics based building game. It combines simple blocks with realistic physics so that everything in the game can be completely destroyed. Build awesome structures, invent machines, master difficult challenges or play exciting multiplayer battles against your friends –', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1lm1.jpg', null),

(34474, 'Bass Blocks', 2015, 'Bass Blocks is a top down RPG shooter, featuring procedurally generated open worlds and interactive music.', null, null),

(34317, 'GravLab - Gravitational Testing Facility & Observations', 2017, 'Build your incredible machine with gravity bending appliances from Grav|Lab! Our new lunar testing facility welcomes you to try out our standardised testing scenarios specifically - now designed for humans!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co26wn.jpg', null),

(34431, 'Rescue Team 3', 2015, 'Save the day as the leader of the Rescue Team, a group of life-saving pros trained to swoop in and sweep up in the wake of a natural disaster! Figure out the quickest way to complete your goals, make good use your resources and unlock every achievement. Easy to play, challenging to master and packed with fun, Rescue Team 3 is the best one yet!', null, null),

(34290, 'Phantom Brave PC', 2016, 'In the year of 921, in a world called Ivoire, lives Marona, a 13 year old orphaned girl with a special ability to communicate with phantoms. Marona believes in her parents` teachings that people will one day come to like her as long as she stays compassionate and kind. 
Now Marona travels throughout Ivoire with her guardian, “Ash the Phantom”, to resolve disputes around the world.', null, null),

(34168, 'Farm Mania: Hot Vacation', 2015, 'This time you’re given a unique opportunity to take part in challenging farming contests held in different parts of the world. Spend the greatest vacation ever traveling around Australia, Egypt and China, look after rare animals and take care of exotic plants!', null, null),

(34247, 'Tales [PC]', 2016, 'When an ancient curse is awakened in an old library, Alfred Walsh must travel to the strangest of places to seek help from many great heroes (and lesser ones) in an effort to save our beloved tales!', null, null),

(34302, 'Fist Slash: Of Ultimate Fury', 2015, 'Part man, part blade, all badass – help Fist Slash defeat the evil Dr. X and recover the mystical mirror shards before they`re used to wreak ultimate destruction on the world!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2166.jpg', null),

(34486, 'The Juicer', 2015, 'The game is a cheerful shooter with a user-friendly gameplay in an original setting.', null, null),

(34242, 'Gun Bombers', 2016, 'Grab your pickaxe and enter the mines! Search for treasures and fight against other miners in this fast, round-based multiplayer game (up to 10 players over LAN or internet).', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2186.jpg', 24758),

(34430, 'Rescue Team 2', 2015, 'Rebuild the devastated islands as you take control of the Rescue Team in this fantastic Time Management game! After a terrifying tornado leaves storms through the islands, it`s up to the Rescue Team to save the day and save lives.', null, null),

(34093, 'Rubber Ducky and the Rainbow Gun', 2015, 'Rubber Ducky has found a Rainbow Gun during a rainstorm of colored weaponry! The Spikies love to be zapped with Rainbow Guns - so much, in fact, that they`ll teleport away to tell the other Spikies about it. Follow Rubber Ducky as he spreads laser-ed goodwill in this shooter-meets-plushie-toy romp!', null, null),

(34325, 'Lethe - Episode One', 2016, 'Lethe is a first person adventure with survival horror elements. Explore an atmospheric and frightening world and uncover the dark secrets of your origins.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1opm.jpg', null),

(34133, 'Astrox: Hostile Space Excavation', 2015, 'Exiled to a deep space mining sector, you are left with a crappy ship, a laser, and a small mining beam. It is up to you to survive by working your way through the galaxy. Mine asteroids, refine and trade the ore, buy upgrades for your ship, hunt pirates... you get it.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1j6z.jpg', null),

(34311, 'Faron`s Fate', 2015, 'Faron`s Fate is an action- roguelike about a lone adventurer venturing into a dungeon full of dangerous monsters and rare artifacts. Enter a procedurally generated dungeon, fight for your life, and collect weapons, loot, and armor along the way. By combining components of The Binding of Isaac and The Legend of Zelda with classic RPG elements, Faron`s Fate creates a unique action- packed experience where no two playthroughs are alike.', null, null),

(34150, 'Modbox', 2016, 'Modbox is a VR multiplayer sandbox game - create your own game experiences to play and share with others', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/hvmfycgbndggeyxwdewi.jpg', null),

(34138, 'Recourse', 2016, 'Recourse is a puzzle game with unprecedented puzzle variety. It`s the story of two A.I. units, Sleet and Floe, trying to discover why they are on a seemingly abandoned ice planet. A playable demo is available for the game. Please visit our website for higher quality videos and more in-depth information.', null, null),

(34128, 'Gigachess', 2015, 'Gigachess is a hero defense puzzler on a chess board. Command your party of Knights, Rooks & Bishops against the relentless Pawn onslaught!', null, null),

(34496, 'Nusakana', 2015, 'Nusakana is an open-world JRPG where you date fish girls while trying to solve the island mysteries. Play as a tourist having a full-year vacation on the island, on a mysterious invitation. Will it be a fun holiday or will it be a thrilling adventure? What about the romance? You decide!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1l02.jpg', null),

(34464, 'Lift It', 2017, 'Lift It is a fresh and dynamic game where you have to train your character in order to gain stats.  
Every Gym exercise helps gaining a specific stat.  
Increasing your stats will help you to beat your enemies when travelling from the main island (Gym Island) to the other islands.  
Beat the 8 gym owners in order to get money, that could be used to buy integrators or weapons.  
You can also fight against other players in a 1 vs 1 sword fight!', null, null),

(34124, 'BAD END', 2015, 'It`s rumored that those who play `BAD END`- a Visual Novel will die in REAL LIFE if they make the wrong decision in the game itself.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/ktuqml93grpequlsbal5.jpg', null),

(34157, 'Turtle Odyssey', 2015, 'Help a brave little turtle get his shell back in this exciting adventure.', null, null),

(34164, 'Bullet Heaven 2', 2015, 'Bullet Heaven 2 is a bullet-hell shoot-em-up inspired by games like Touhou and Jamestown. 
It`s all about shooting every cute thing that moves, while dodging hundreds of shiny bullets per second!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2kbf.jpg', null),

(34131, 'Crashnauts', 2018, 'Crashnauts is a hard-hitting 2D platform shooter for up to 4 players local or online. Quickplay online, or connect directly with friends in a custom match. Crash into objective based gameplay with scrolling levels and hazards. Fluid combat and brutal weapons make for a fresh experience every match.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co28wu.jpg', null),

(34364, 'Monsterland', 2015, 'Monsterland is an MS-DOS-style textmode shooter with a story-driven campaign which is about 3 hours long. As you blast your way through the levels, finding keycards and unlocking doors, you are faced with increasingly frantic battles with a variety of Monsters.', null, null),

(34084, 'Viking Saga: New World', 2015, 'Travel to the far lands of the west! Visit wondrous corners of the ancient world! Meet new interesting characters and learn their intriguing stories! Find a cure and save your kingdom!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co224r.jpg', null),

(34188, 'VROOM: Galleon', 2015, 'Experience virtual life at sea aboard a pirate ship!', null, null),

(34062, 'Northern Tale', 2016, 'A beautiful legend filled with magic, bravery and amazing adventures!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co21ee.jpg', null),

(34037, 'SculptrVR', 2016, 'Welcome to VR’s first must-play world-building experience. SculptrVR makes it easy to create, explore, and share brilliant new worlds together with friends. Build at massive scale or shrink down to add tiny details. With SculptrVR’s intuitive tools, your imagination makes anything possible.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/ihcj8hsf2dxdfixdr2zy.jpg', null),

(34392, 'Disgaea PC', 2016, 'A version of Disgaea: Hour of Darkness, including the added content in Afternoon of Darkness, was released for Microsoft Windows via Steam on February 24, 2016, retitled as Disgaea PC. The initial release was panned by critics on launch due to its many bugs, which included persistent crashes, save file loss, and poor performance, even on high-end PCs. A patch was released soon afterwards that fixed many of the bugs. Another patch was released for the game later that added the four characters previously exclusive to Disgaea DS. Players who bought the game during the 2016 Steam Summer Sale would also earn free in-game cosmetic items for Valve’s first person shooter game Team Fortress 2.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1tvw.jpg', null),

(34140, 'Run Turn Die', 2016, 'Your heart racing. Your fingers tense. Your mind empty of thoughts. All that exists, is the path in front of you. You sit on the edge of the chair. Will you make it this time?', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co20zz.jpg', 24720),

(34231, 'Fantasy Farming: Orange Season', 2017, 'Orange Season is a farm-life RPG, focused on exploration and different gameplay mechanics.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co237k.jpg', null),

(34003, 'Holodance', 2016, 'Get your workout with any osu!-beatmap in pure rhythm game environments, or immerse yourself - guided by dragons - in the mindset that will save our lovely little planet ... in the only room-scale Virtual Reality rhythm game that precisely knows each note of every song in the game!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/fiuhmgsp62lfaxnc2mrl.jpg', null),

(34416, 'This Book Is A Dungeon', 2015, 'Auto-cannibalism. Demonic Seduction. Occult Rituals. Bloodfeasting Worms. This dark, horrific Twine-based dungeon crawler pairs edgy interactive fiction with grisly pixel art and light RPG elements. Navigate this sprawling narrative-driven labyrinth bristling with otherworldly doom.', null, null),

(34076, 'Cally`s Caves 3', 2016, 'Cally`s parents have been abducted, as her arch-enemy Herbert has taken control of the Caves to perform his evil experiments. Join Cally and her friends in this action-packed run and gun platformer, conquering insane bosses, exploring to find secrets, and levelling up EVERYTHING. 
Use your weapons to level them up and evolve them into their ultimate forms! Unlock new character abilities like the Triple Jump, Dodge Roll and Water Wings. Use a second playable character, Bera to unleash crazy awesome ninja moves and solve challenging puzzles. Most importantly, battle to rescue your parents from Herbert`s clutches, and bring an end to Herbert`s experiments for good!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/aumbxbgdg7nejkapbztc.jpg', null),

(34015, 'BLARP!', 2016, 'BLARP! is a fun-filled physics game build for the HTC Vive. BLARP! uses our intuitive understanding of motions and physics to create an active / addictive experience that is playable by anyone who has ever swung a racket, played with a yoyo, or held a rope.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/qrwmpmluo0cnjofihhvr.jpg', null),

(34454, 'ChargeShot', 2015, 'Shoot, reflect, and jetpack your way through ChargeShot -- a local-multiplayer, space-bounty-hunter, deathmatch game with a focus on fast-paced, twitch gameplay. Prove to your friends that you are the greatest warrior in the galaxy. No friends? No problem. Progress through the challenging, single-player campaign to unlock achievements and claim your spot on the global leaderboards.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1ocd.jpg', null),

(34300, 'Unfortunate Spacemen', 2020, 'Unfortunate Spacemen is a multiplayer game about space-based murder in space! Spacemen work diligently to be rescued from their failing outpost, but not everyone is who they claim to be...', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co29qg.jpg', null),

(34332, 'SAVAGE: The Shard of Gosen', null, 'A 2D action/platforming adventure with a healthy dose of RPG elements set in the hostile world of Lor, a pre-history fantasy setting. The slave-hungry Argeshii empire dominates the known world, old and false gods conspire; brutal combat is the only means of survival!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1q4f.jpg', 17000),

(34334, 'Swarm Universe', 2017, 'A highly modifiable top-down shooter featuring highscore-driven singleplayer challenges and online-multiplayer competition. You get arenas, racetracks, mini-games and various online-multiplayer modes. Plus powerful modding-tools to create your own levels and game-modes.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co24v7.jpg', null),

(34328, 'Hyper Bounce Blast', 2016, 'Hyper Bounce Blast is a stomach-churning retro shooter blended with classic platforming action. Bounce, shoot and dodge to survive the ever-increasing enemy attack. Bring it on!', null, null),

(34429, 'Silver Creek Falls - Chapter 2', 2015, 'One week after the eerie events occurred in Silver Creek Falls, the sleepy town in North Carolina is hit with yet another tragedy. An FBI agent is brutally murdered in cold blood in his own bedroom. No one knows who did it or why. Only one thing is clear: something truly sinister is broiling in Silver Creek Falls. 
 
Play as Boston-born detective Sara Fitzgerald, as she continues her investigation of this creepy town and unfurls a plot far more convoluted and intricate than she could ever imagine!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/lmiofyrxmtgxeurob03h.jpg', null),

(34447, 'Zero Punctuation: Hatfall - Hatters Gonna Hat Edition', 2015, 'HATFALL is a high-energy game of skill and hat-wearing born from Zero Punctuation, the hit online video series from The Escapist, created by the man behind ZP, Ben `Yahtzee` Croshaw.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/wh9gaznyeo99oxj1p0zz.jpg', null),

(34059, 'Mayjasmine episode01 What is God? 五月茉莉', 2015, 'Ho Yu-Chen received his friend Wan Zi-Jin`s invitation, and set on to leave the familiar Taiwan to start a new life with Wan`s daughter, Wan Yu-Qing, as an accountant, in Indonesia. Yet with the addition of the mysterious girl, Cocoa, what kinds of events shall turn out to be?', null, null),

(34074, 'Turbo Pug', 2015, 'It`s time to unleash your inner pug! 
Turbo Pug is a casual runner with difficult, random, procedurally generated levels. 
Enjoy random weather and try to avoid getting zapped by lightning. 
Unlock new costumes for your pug and new characters to play as. 
Please try not to squish your pug!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/c2ktswnwluakqnebtarm.jpg', null),

(34254, 'Warhammer: Vermintide VR - Hero Trials', 2016, 'Step into the Warhammer Fantasy world like never before in this short and fun VR experience. As an aspiring hero, you need to prove your worth by outsmarting the cunning Skaven, using your expert marksmanship and keen melee skills. For the Empire!', null, null),

(34658, 'Blasted Road Terror', 2018, 'Blasted Road Terror is real-time tactical looter in post apocalyptic setting. Command mighty warcrawler and manage squadron of vehicles in order to get unseen riches of the world and reach immortal glory. You will collect mighty arctifacts during your journey, enlarge your vehicle squadron so you can always pick right one for the job, rebuild your home base, make new friends and discover terrible enemies.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co23w9.jpg', null),

(34756, 'Collisions', 2015, 'Collisions is a relaxing puzzle game set in a beautiful environment. The puzzles vary from one screen to the next: some are easy, others require timing, logic and anticipation.', null, null),

(34883, 'Space - The Return Of The Pixxelfrazzer', 2015, 'Space - The Return Of The Pixxelfrazzer is an open-world sci-fi hack`n`slash. Your aim is to explore the inexhaustible amounts of destructible asteroid fields, spacestations and unknown planets of the universe. And maybe, one day you`ll probably find out about one of the most unsolved mystery of our universe... the pixxelfrazzer.', null, null),

(34887, 'Ninjahtic', 2015, 'Ninjahtic is an action/adventure platformer with elements of puzzle-solving and stealth. While it`s progression is linear, the open-ended nature of every level requires exploration of an abandoned civilization located atop floating islands. Usage of the environment also plays a key role when solving puzzles and dispatching enemy robots throughout.', null, null),

(34577, 'Guided Meditation VR', 2016, 'Meditation made simple & visual, built from the ground up for VR. Leave the worries of your life for a short virtual vacation across 17 environments, and return calmer and stronger. Find your happy place.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/lueiqtcjic650gldc3nq.jpg', null),

(34939, 'Eco', 2018, 'Eco is an online global-survival world from Strange Loop Games, where players must build civilization using resources from an ecosystem that can be damaged and destroyed. The world of Eco is an incredibly reactive one, and whatever any player does in the world affects the underlying ecosystem. As a group you can make laws regarding the world, in order to protect its sensitive ecosystem. The game can also be played offline, if the player prefers to do so.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1wlv.jpg', 4373),

(34656, 'Rot Gut', 2016, 'Rot Gut is an action packed platformer set in America’s 1920’s Prohibition era. You take control of an agent who, to uncover their mysteries, goes on a mission to fight the city’s underground armed to the teeth organizations.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/b8cxmxwu1gofw45lqwsz.jpg', null),

(34959, 'Boss 101', 2017, 'Boss 101 is an action adventure game with you taking the role of Max, a teenager with a jetpack. Help your brother and save the world at the same time. Buy weapons, hats, upgrades while you battle millions of randomly generated bosses.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co29zm.jpg', null),

(34873, 'The Beard in the Mirror', 2016, 'A point-and-click adventure filled with magic, danger, fantasy, and romance.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/ozv6oefi2nzxrwvp0zuw.jpg', null),

(34599, 'World`s Fastest Pizza', 2016, 'Head to Australia and use all the superpowers you can to deliver fast pizza! Watch out for pizza-haters though! World`s Fastest Pizza: It`s not easy, when your pizza is so cheesy...', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/kvqk0a3rl5zmeunq2vfq.jpg', 16906),

(34895, 'STLD Redux: Episode 02', 2017, 'Formulate a strategy and strike back with your own cunning and intelligence as you`re forced into the original nightmarish scenario we`ve all dreamed about. Will you be ready when the dead break down the doors?', null, null),

(34898, 'Hack Run ZERO', 2015, 'It`s time for a SECOND Hack Run! Test your skills again as you hack your way through strange and secretive organizations to discover their hidden agendas! Hack Run ZERO uses old school prompts (like dos and unix) to help you navigate from system to system. As you access users` accounts, you`ll discover more and more about the organizations and the people that work there.  
 
Your adventure begins when you receive a disturbing ransom note about a loved one. Your only way to set them free is to follow the kidnapper`s shady demands. Once again your mission is to penetrate the maze of computer accounts through the use of your hacking skills. The stakes run high as you uncover more and more of the enemy`s diabolical plan; and with over 70 levels there`s no guessing how it will all end!', null, null),

(34718, 'Trigonarium', 2015, 'Trigonarium is a hardcore twin-stick shooter for fans of challenging arcade gaming. Fight your way through multitudes of enemy formations in constantly shifting battle arenas to face the colossal level bosses.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/eo60y3tflvzwwabddva2.jpg', null),

(34762, 'Farm Frenzy Collection', 2015, 'Enjoy the farmhouse gems with this solid set of 12 Farm Frenzy titles! 
Join Scarlett throughout all of her adventures in hundreds of farming challenges. Raise chickens, ostriches, and dolphins. Bake cakes, grow crops, and sell items at markets. It`s an all-out farming assault with one of the most enjoyed series ever!', null, null),

(34728, 'Alien Attack: In Space', 2016, 'You are a space trooper. Somehow you got to the enemy territory, and you should wait for your squad to get out of here! But only God knows when will they arrive to you! They will send you bonuses for killed enemies to longer your life till they arrive.', null, null),

(34755, 'Angry Arrows', 2015, 'Angry Arrows is a cooperative archery game about rescuing hostages from enemy strongholds using nothing but bows and arrows. Just remember, one fatal mistake and it`s back to square one.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co23p4.jpg', null),

(34752, 'Steel Ocean', 2015, 'It is a free-to-play shooting game.You may choose 6 types of warships used in the WWII to play PvP and PvE naval battle. Start the voyage with your warships and fight for the honor of your fleet!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/nb7xdias8qtbxsgvs8pu.jpg', null),

(34536, 'Mooch', 2015, 'Mooch is an arcade experience where player must rely only on his reflex and agility. 
Main protagonist is puppet Blink who starts dangerous mission to find soul pieces of his friend Tula. 
Watch your every step. Even passages that seem safe may hide deadly traps. Puppet Master`s machines are constantly lurking for the hero and his only way to survive is to outsmart them.', null, null),

(34529, 'Hoven the Sages Spinel', 2015, 'Welcome to the world of Hoven! Join Bradley and his friends on an adventure that transforms into an epic quest! Traverse dangerous dungeons and battle fearsome foes. Discover the truth about who you are and what you have to do to save the world from the evil sage, Maluma! The fate of hoven hangs in the balance, will you rise to the challenge?', null, null),

(34871, 'Wave Mechanics', 2015, 'The goal of Wave Mechanics is to match the color of each element to the colors of corresponding parts of the frame. Each puzzle includes a set of active elements that can by used in order to change the colors of all elements within range in chosen direction.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/pck4lvprwjxxcvtukyl5.jpg', null),

(34562, 'Moonstrider', 2015, 'Moonstrider is an action roguelike about shipwrecked astronauts trying to survive the journey back to Earth. Leap between planets with your trusty rocket boots, gather powerful items, fight against deadly and cunning aliens, and discover what really stranded you in the depths of space.', null, null),

(34580, 'MachineCraft', 2016, 'The main purpose of this game is showing and watching machines made out of blocks. 
