(34500, 'Straima', 2015, 'Straima is a devilishly difficult pulse-pumper platformer for 1-4 players. It includes several game modes, selectable powers and gameplay mutators, as well as a full feature level editor allowing you to design, save and share your inspired creations with chums for immense joy.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1tla.jpg', null),

