(35272, 'Lilly and Sasha: Nexus of Souls', 2015, 'Zahhak has Sasha`s body and is going to use it to claim the powers of the Immortals. Lilly has vowed to stop Zahhak at whatever cost, even if she has to kill her own sister to do it. 
 
