(35216, 'Samsa and the Knights of Light', 2015, 'Samsa and the Knights of Light is a RPG game, with 2D retro-style. The game takes you into the story of SAMSA, a strong but lazy demon who wants to save the world, his way. While going against a society that judges him for every action, SAMSA can show that you shouldn`t judge a book for it`s cover. 
 
