(35528, 'Space Beast Terror Fright', 2015, 'S.B.T.F. is a very hard arcade-style / rogue-like / perma-death first person shooter. You play as Marines who must brave dark, claustrophobic and terrifyingly intense Space Beast infested spacecraft in order to extract critical data and lucrative upgrades. Can you make it out alive?', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co28hg.jpg', null),

(35612, 'ENIGMA: An Illusion Named Family', 2015, 'The hero of the game, Minhyuk, loses his father in an accident in his childhood. He spends his adolescence in guilt, while his siblings jump into a family feud over the inheritance.One day, an unexpected blackout takes place in the mansion, and Minhyuk has to overcome the strange and often fatal incidents to find out the truth behind.', null, null),

(35824, 'Gran Vitreous', 2015, 'Gran Vitreous is a PC shmup that combines classic arena shooter gameplay with the mechanics of a loot driven action RPG. Upgrade your ships equipment and level up as you battle through a galaxy filled with randomly generated encounters.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/bpz48te8vyuhhfdc8ee2.jpg', null),

