(36319, 'Rise of Prussia Gold', 2014, 'Rise of Prussia Gold is the new and improved version of AGEODs Seven Years War (1757-1763) game set in Europe. This hugely detailed strategy game was initially released by AGEOD in 2010 and the Gold version adds numerous improvements and additional scenarios that take the game to the next level.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1ymb.jpg', null),

