(38796, 'Star Fleet Armada: Rogue Adventures', 2017, 'Captain a fleet of ships. Meet new races. Explore other star systems. Discover and explore anomalies, asteroid fields, nebulas, suns, comets and more. Can you find that rare Rainbow planet that is teeming with mass amounts of resources?  Play as any of the 45 races. Earn Achievements to get rare in game artifacts!', null, null),

(38787, 'Kartong', 2017, 'Kartong - Death by Cardboard! This "cute" FPS stealth game puts you up against evil experiments inside a miniature cardboard city. The maze of traps changes with every game, paper cuts are deadly and Mr Chuckles is very ANGRY. But hey, who doesn’t love the smell of cardboard in the morning?', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2bsj.jpg', null),

(38755, 'Dead Exit', 2017, 'Dead Exit is an undead apocalypse, base management, card game. Play alone, with friends, or against friends. Just play smart and make sure you get the resources you need to escape the city.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2aqa.jpg', null),

(38629, 'Legendary Hunter VR', 2017, 'Legendary Hunter VR is a VR duck hunting game inspired by the old classic NES game Duck Hunt. Hunt Duck during the day time while surviving vicious crow attacks .And survive the wolves and the crocodiles at night . Enjoy the day / night cycles with dynamic weather and atmospheric surround sound .', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co253g.jpg', null),

(40466, 'Disco Time 80s VR', 2017, 'The 80s are back! Enter the Dancefloor and celebrate an 80s club party in VR.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2at0.jpg', null),

(40139, 'Stayin` Alive', 2018, 'Do your best to die, or to save your enemies from death in this frantic multiplayer game about life and death. 2 Maps, 4 vs. 4 matches, death is in the air.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1qc0.jpg', null),

(40708, 'Chambered', 2017, 'Chambered is a single-player, story-based VR shooting game with an emphasis on weapon progression. Featuring trackpad locomotion, 13 guns, and 140+ weapon mods, Chambered is sure to keep you playing for hours.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2ahj.jpg', null),

(40521, 'Airtone', 2017, '"From an all-star team of industry veterans comes Airtone, the Air Rhythm Action experience that brings true rhythm gaming into the VR scene! 
 
