(43121, 'Pinball Wicked', 2017, 'One of the world`s most advanced virtual pinball simulations featuring original table #1: Black Flaggers - a pirate’s journey of plundering loot, swashbuckling adventures and cannon wielding foes. Wicked pinball mechanics on a cutting edge engine: the high fidelity pinball experience.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co24qb.jpg', null),

