(50834, 'Yu-Gi-Oh! Power of Chaos: Yugi the Destiny', 2003, 'The first Yu-Gi-Oh! game for PC and the first of the three Power of Chaos games. The game includes 155 cards which most of them are from Legend of Blue Eyes White Dragon and Starter Deck: Yugi. Two are from Metal Raiders. One is from Spell Ruler, another is from Tournament Pack: 3rd Season, and the other is from Starter Deck: Pegasus. 
 
