(53310, 'Botlike - a robot`s rampage', 2018, 'Botlike - loot and shoot your way through hordes of robots or die trying. Play as S.I.R. - a grumpy old warbot on his path to revenge. Use your ever-growing arsenal of weapons, upgrades and powerful items to defeat an evil and totalitarian robot league. Grab your top hat and let the rampage begin.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co23w8.jpg', null),

