(54631, 'Cat Sorter VR', 2017, 'This wacky VR party game is great for just about anyone. Finally a Vive room-scale game where you get to sort cats and compete for the highest score!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2agt.jpg', null),

(54886, 'Space Pilgrim Academy', 2017, 'Latona Research Station has been destroyed by unknown assailants. The only survivor is a young girl who was rescued by the Starship Quicksilver and her renowned captain.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1zmt.jpg', null),

(54828, 'Zombie Solitaire 2 Chapter 2', 2017, 'Your crazy survival odyssey continues. Play your cards right and use your sugar ammo wisely to escape from the zombie epidemic!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co272b.jpg', null),

(54736, 'Autonauts', 2019, 'You are responsible for colonising uninhabited planets. Start from nothing and harness natural resources to build a robot empire that can be taught anything. Automation is the name of the game - progress through the technological ages, automate life itself and achieve absolute autonomy!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1sck.jpg', null),

(54984, 'Mewnbase', 2018, 'MewnBase is a cute, 2D exploration/survival game. You land on an uncharted world only to realize you didn`t bring any snacks and forgot half your luggage. But hey, at least you brought this workbench thing. You`ll need to collect resources in order to construct a make-shift base. Craft a variety of different base modules, from airlocks to rain-water collectors in order to make your new home on this barren planet a little more cozy.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1mtj.jpg', null),

(54825, 'Chocolate', 2017, 'Chocolate is a 3-4 minute reactive linear VR music video experience for the song by Giraffage that sets you as a robot in a cat-centric world of colorful chrome in which your hands interact with your environment and everything dynamically moves and changes to the music.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2aig.jpg', null),

(54831, '1bitHeart', 2017, 'Welcome to 1bitHeart―the latest title from Alicemare and LiEat developer △○□× (Miwashiba). In this unique and endearing adventure game, take on the role of Nanashi, a lonely, agoraphobic boy, as you solve a slew of mysteries around town while also making friends.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1ptj.jpg', null),

