(55231, 'The Little Ball That Could', 2017, 'The Little Ball That Could is a unique marble platformer that will test your skill and your curiosity! One moment, you`ll be dodging lasers as you`re looking for the lost gems; the next, you`ll be doing crazy aerial acrobatics to reach the switch that sets your friend free!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co23df.jpg', 18960),

(55224, 'Air Tactical', 2017, 'You are a spaceship pilot who wants to break out of all this chaos. Manage your spaceship, destroy everything in its path. Collect bonuses and pump your spaceship.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co29er.jpg', null),

(55406, 'Undead Development', 2018, 'How long would you survive in this unrealistic representation of the zombie apocalypse? 
