(55488, 'D`LIRIUM', 2017, 'An experimental 2D-shooter with the elements of a horror game. D`lirium brings together some mechanics back from 90s classics. Non-linear levels, search for the keys, violence and a lot of other things. Including the colourful ponies.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co26ur.jpg', null),

