(55299, 'Supersonic Tank Cats', 2017, 'Supersonic Tank Cats is a fast race-and-battle karts game featuring unconventional half-kitty and half-combat vehicles. Move in cartoony racetracks as you use hilarious weapons against your rivals to reach the goal before anyone else.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1k2f.jpg', null),

