Now realised with the power of cutting-edge technology for Windows PCs, including support for high-resolution displays and HDR10, the beautiful and carefully-crafted experience of FINAL FANTASY XV can be explored like never before."', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co205r.jpg', null),

(55347, 'Oswald`s Adventure', 2017, 'Follow Oswald in his adventure to find his sister. Will he find her? Or is there a surprise waiting for him? There is only one way to find out! Good luck, adventurers.', null, null),

(55486, '0°N 0°W', 2018, 'A cross country road trip turns into a multi-dimensional walkabout after a quick stop in a mysterious town. A first person surreal adventure of visual auditory stimuli set in a fantastical world.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co28r7.jpg', null),

(55036, 'Anno 1800', 2019, 'Welcome to the dawn of the industrial age. The path you choose will define your world. Are you renovator or exploiter? Suppressor or liberator? It`s up to you how the world will remember your name. 
 
