(55408, 'MarZ: Tactical Base Defense', 2017, 'MarZ Rising is a tactical base defense game, which lets you discover a completely new gameplay experience of the tower defense genre! Build, manage and defend your martian base. Guide your crew safely through the thrilling campaign and solve the mystery of the undead.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1p7u.jpg', 16274),

(55056, 'Age of Empires II: Definitive Edition', 2019, 'Age of Empires II: Definitive Edition celebrates the 20th anniversary of one of the most popular strategy games ever with stunning 4K Ultra HD graphics, a new and fully remastered soundtrack, and brand-new content, “The Last Khans” with 3 new campaigns and 4 new civilizations.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1n24.jpg', null),

(55804, 'Manifest 99', 2017, 'MANIFEST 99 is an ominous and eerie VR story set on a train rumbling through the afterlife. Accompanied by a murder of crows and four mysterious travel companions, you must uncover the reason why they – and you – are on this train traveling into the great beyond. Gaze into their eyes and discover the remnants of their weary souls, before they pass on.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co277k.jpg', null),

