This is a very interesting and exciting game! Don`t trust?', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co26ua.jpg', null),

(56655, 'Attack Of Insects', 2017, 'Love insects? And insects that are two or even ten times more than you? If you love, then - it`s fine, you will definitely be pleased with our insects. And if you do not love, then you will be happy, because you have to shoot on insects and watch them fly apart!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co29ul.jpg', null),

(56868, 'Catan VR', 2018, 'VR enabled rendition of the board game classic.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co28wa.jpg', null),

(56606, 'ProjectM : Daydream', 2017, 'Experience a daydream like never before in VR. Experience skydiving, hang out at the beach, or just chat with a digital friend in the comfort of a virtual kitchen.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2hn1.jpg', null),

(56982, 'Wands', 2017, 'Wands is a PVP spellcasting game for Samsung Gear VR and Google DayDream devices.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co24km.jpg', null),

(56600, 'Eternal Lore', 2017, 'Eternal Lore is a classic Action-RPG Game where the player can explore the world and dungeons while battling monsters and 
bosses, solving puzzles during the adventure and collect items to craft powerful equipment and gain access to even more powerful 
skills during your adventure.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co26vp.jpg', null),

(56651, 'DeathComing', 2017, '《Death Coming》is a pixel-style non-linear puzzle game. You became a “death agent” via a dramatic death. You may experience the Death job and reap souls in the cities. But what lies behind the scenes? Can you control your own fate?', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co26sp.jpg', null),

(56623, '仙剑奇侠传四-Chinese Paladin 4', 2017, '《仙剑奇侠传四》是由软星科技（上海）有限公司研发，北京新游时代网络技术有限公司发行代理的角色扮演单机游戏，也是系列单机游戏《仙剑奇侠传》的第五部作品', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co277v.jpg', null),

(56602, 'BRKÖUT', 2017, 'Classic brick breaking action with a bizarre twist. Play the game from another time and place.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2a0o.jpg', null),

(56622, 'NOISZ', 2017, 'From devs who worked on Pump It Up Infinity, NeonFM, and more: NOISZ combines rhythm gameplay with bullet hell shoot-em-ups for a unique challenge!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co24zy.jpg', null),

(56675, 'L.S.S', 2017, 'You are sent in on top secret missions across the world to erase any existence of the governments tests. 
BUT things don`t seem to go to plan as you are forced to fight for your life in a hope you will make it out alive!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co274d.jpg', null),

(56620, 'Into the Rhythm VR', 2017, 'Into the Rhythm VR is a drumming experience brought to virtual reality. You are given drum sticks along with 6 drums. Follow the dropping notes to play the awesome music you always wanted. All you need is a place to sit, and motion controllers to strike with rhythm!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2bq7.jpg', null),

(56867, 'NVIDIA® VR Funhouse', 2016, 'Step right up to VR Funhouse and enter a virtual carnival full of fun and games. Be an archer with flaming arrows. Test your skill shooting skeet targets blasted from a cannon. See how many moles you can punch, whack, and much more.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1zwn.jpg', 1630),

(56873, 'Duck Season', 2017, 'The game of your dreams just dropped, DUCK SEASON, a hunter with ridiculous graphics. Luckily, it`s summer vacation and Mom just surprised you with a one day rental of it! Unfortunately, as you binge play it becomes apparent that all is not right with Duck Season...', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1o4n.jpg', null),

(56696, 'Wolfpack', 2019, 'Wolfpack is a co-op U-boat simulation game.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2h5c.jpg', null),

(56613, 'Mad Age And This Guy', 2017, 'This is the age of steam. This is the time of unprecedented technology development never seen before. This is the era of science, research, and inventions. However, this world has also another side, the side not everyone aware of. This world is full of mad scientists who plan to use modern technology for the evil purpose – they want to take over the world. But when evil and deception grow in strength, he will appear. He is the secret agent of an elite unit which has to make sure that the newest science inventions do not fall into the wrong hands.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co27yw.jpg', null),

(56553, 'CPU Invaders', 2017, 'CPU Invaders', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2alf.jpg', null),

(56639, 'Mike Dies', 2018, 'Mike Dies is a challenging fast-paced exploration-platformer with dynamic brutal fatalities and a massive non-linear environment. After flying his spaceship into an asteroid field, Mike finds himself fighting for survival against hostile aliens, a ruthless kingpin and his own personal demons.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co27m9.jpg', null),

(56649, 'Durak!', 2017, 'Durak is a classical Russian card game. While it requires strategical thinking, cheating is also a viable strategy as long as you don`t get caught. In the same spirit pay attention to your opponents or else you might get tricked and be left as the Durak! The game is best enjoyed with 1 to 5 friends.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co26vc.jpg', null),

(57268, 'Punch Planet', 2017, 'Punch Planet is a sci-fi themed indie fighting game.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co24r0.jpg', null),

(57372, 'SoulWorker', 2016, 'Soulworker is an anime action MMORPG which takes place in the Cloudrealm, a now vacant city which only harbors the psychics and a horde of monsters. Players will learn about the fate of the city and the reason for the disappearance of all inhabitants through the course of the game, as well as possibly finding a way to reverse this catastrophe.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1mvu.jpg', null),

(57217, 'IRONSIGHT', 2019, 'Set in a dystopian 2025, where the warring factions, the North Atlantic Federation (NAF) and the Energy Development Enterprise Network (EDEN) are engaged in futuristic warfare in the final battle over the last natural resources on the planet.  
 
Ironsight puts you in the middle of a global war between international corporations and elite mercenaries. You are thrown on the forefront of a technologically advanced battlefield. Armed with the most innovative weaponry and drone systems, you`re prepared for the final futuristic battle on Earth. 
 
In this realistic FPS, immerse yourself in intense combat zones set across a multitude of global landmarks, with varying terrain and weather conditions.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1v2k.jpg', null),

(57391, 'Major\Minor', 2016, 'Visual Novel game about a wave of murders that sweep across a city.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/f70ay3ltw7k82cip3nod.jpg', null),

(57834, 'The Shattering', 2020, 'The Shattering is a first-person, story-driven, psychological thriller that takes place in the pristine white aesthetic of protagonist John Evans’ own dream. Players must piece together the fragments of the past and present, following the voice of the ‘Doctor’ as he guides them deeper into John’s mind. 
 
Players will experience the key moments of John’s life that have defined and shaped him – they will be tasked with discovering the truth, shattering the lies and, ultimately, finding out what happened to him… and to remember her name.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2m7k.jpg', null),

(58407, 'Regular Human Basketball', 2018, 'Ready to play some ball? Grab a team, suit up, and climb inside your human! Prep its thrusters, lower the all-terrain wheels, and spin up that flailing magnet-arm. It`s time to play Regular Human Basketball!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1n37.jpg', null),

(58544, 'Rain of Reflections', null, 'Rain of Reflections is an atmospheric, dystopian adventure game. Its turn-based strategic confrontations are uniquely centered around a motivation mechanic. Every move and choice made by the player is permanent and will have consequences on the world and its characters.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1ql6.jpg', 15618),

(59258, 'Lance A Lot: Enhanced Edition', 2017, 'Challenge up to four your friends to a glorious duel of rocket jousting! Settle rivalries and become the last knight standing in this fast paced local multiplayer!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co274u.jpg', null),

(59260, 'Sidewords', 2017, 'Grab a cup of coffee and relax with Sidewords. Sidewords is part logic puzzle, part word game, all original. No timers. No penalties. No pressure. Just you and a good puzzle.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co24sy.jpg', null),

(59232, 'Echo Grotto', 2017, 'Echo Grotto is a virtual reality experience that lets you explore unique and intricate cave systems using a range of caving gear and tools!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co24ih.jpg', null),

(59250, 'This Grand Life', 2017, 'In This Grand Life, you create a character, manage their finances and help them achieve their goals. Cruise your way through life with a silver spoon, or struggle endlessly to find employment as a convicted felon. You cannot control your past, but you can change your future. What choices will you make?', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/pdxgjfug20vrmegs2g3j.jpg', null),

(59240, 'Ne no Kami - The Two Princess Knights of Kyoto Part 2', 2017, 'Kyoto is shrouded in silence. 
 
While the Ayakashi change course and prepare themselves for invasion, a sudden turn of events suddenly has Len drawing her sword against Shinonome. What brought upon this drastic course of events?', null, null),

(59245, 'Star Shelter', 2017, 'You`re stranded in space. You must explore, scavenge, craft, hack and fight to survive. You must arm and upgrade your spaceship in order to escape this cosmic graveyard.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/t7sfmhyxqoylgprcwknl.jpg', null),

(59774, 'Grapple Force Rena', 2018, 'Swing, climb, grab, and throw in this action platformer where you can grapple anywhere! Using Rena`s magic bracelets, hook onto any surface to swing wherever you like, or grab your foes to send them hurtling into each other!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1qpu.jpg', null),

(59613, 'Vestaria Saga', 2016, 'Vestaria Saga is an indie Japanese SRPG by Shouzou Kaga, creator of the Fire Emblem series. It is the third game in the Tear Ring Saga series. 
 
"Vestaria Saga is a classically styled Strategy RPG, where positioning, movement, and even weaponry, are paramount to success. Move your heavily armed units around a classic styled grid-based map and engage pirates, rebels, monsters, imperial soldiers, and anyone else that stands in your way."', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1ofd.jpg', 16190),

(59528, 'Gary Grigsby`s War in the West', 2014, 'Based on the War in the East engine with years of additional major features and improvements, Gary Grigsby’s War in the West 1943-45 is the most ambitious and detailed computer wargame on the Western Front of World War II ever made. Starting with the Summer 1943 invasions of Sicily and Italy and proceeding through the invasions of France and the drive into Germany, War in the West brings you all the Allied campaigns in Western Europe and the capability to re-fight the Western Front according to your plan.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1ymm.jpg', null),

(60155, 'Sakura Fantasy: Chapter 1', 2015, 'An entry in the Sakura franchise, this time with a female protagonist.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1u13.jpg', null),

(60212, 'Cogmind', 2017, 'Cogmind is a sci-fi roguelike epic in which you play a robot building yourself from components found or salvaged from other robots. Explore a living, breathing world through turn-based tactical combat, or sneak, hack, and fly your way to victory.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1udx.jpg', 18488),

(61469, 'Hoshizora no Memoria -Wish upon a Shooting Star-', 2009, 'After their mother passes away, Kogasaka You and his younger sister, Chinami, pack up and move out of the city back to their hometown of Hibarigasaki to live with their aunt Shino. Before making the move to the city, You spent almost every single day after school playing with a girl up at the town observation lookout; she was You`s first true friend. And when she learns of You’s upcoming relocation to the city she becomes very upset…so much so that she makes him promise to her that one day he must return to Hibarigasaki to marry her. And with a final departure she kisses You on the forehead. 
 
Years later, upon returning to Hibarigasaki, You comes across a now abandoned, fenced-off observatory lookout. It is at this lookout where he encounters a mysterious scythe-wielding girl named Mare who looks strangely like his childhood friend from years past. But as You`s life back in his hometown progresses, he is able to makes new friends both in the astronomy club at school and while working at a local restaurant, all while still attempting to seek out his childhood friend. Intrigued, he continues to visit with this mysterious girl at the lookout, but who is she really, and will he ever be able to find his childhood friend and make good on his promise? 
 
An updated version of the game was released in 2019 titled Hoshizora no Memoria HD, an anniversary celebration of the game`s first launch in 2009. It includes redrawn CGs from 4:3 to 16:9 and a rearranged OST.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2fcu.jpg', null),

(61602, 'HellTown', 2017, 'The year is 1959, you just got a job as a postman in a brand new town called Little Vale. Although the sun is shining and the birds are chirping, this town is shrouded in mystery. Something… unnatural is afoot here.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2blf.jpg', null),

(61714, 'To Leave', 2018, 'Indie platformer about a boy who seeks to leave his old life behind using a magical flying door. 
 
To Leave features challenging puzzle-platformer levels that will test your puzzle-solving skills through an emotionally gripping story. The game addresses depression – a state of mind that tempts you to open any doors if they allow you to leave everything behind … sometimes for a moment … sometimes for life. 
 
Key Features 
 
- Experience a lyrical, inspiring puzzle-platformer that blurs genre boundaries. 
- Take on grueling challenges and test your problem-solving skills. 
- Follow an emotionally gripping narrative that doesn’t hold back on characters or symbolism. 
- Understand the hardships of depression through a powerful mix of story and gameplay. 
- Enjoy a beautiful handcrafted world.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2inm.jpg', 21023),

(61622, 'Sacralith: The Archer`s Tale', 2017, 'Sacralith: The Archer`s Tale is a breathtaking story of an archer in a world of dark magic and Inquisition. Don`t let your magic abilities to play trick on you - even an invisible warrior may be tracked , so this adventure promises to be the hardest one..', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2360.jpg', null),

(61605, 'Mahjong VR', 2017, 'This is a game playing mahjong in a virtual reality environment', null, null),

(61617, 'The Walking Vegetables', 2017, 'It’s the 1980’s and an evil alien race has invaded Earth, turning all vegetables into crawling, bawling, mauling abominations. You are about to join Department Radical, the grooviest police force on Earth. 
Are you a rad enough dude (or dame) to smite these ravenous creatures?', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co26z7.jpg', null),

(61651, 'Ocean Rift', 2017, 'Ocean Rift is the world`s first VR aquatic safari park. Explore a vivid underwater world full of life including dolphins, sharks, orcas, turtles, sea snakes, rays, manatees, sea lions, whales, and even dinosaurs!', null, null),

(61645, 'One Night You`re Crazy', 2017, 'It`s like playing tag. Where you collect bloody teddy bear parts. While avoiding a flesh eating wolf. Or maybe you`ll be the wolf. I don`t care either way.', null, null),

(61621, 'Temple of Aluxes', 2017, 'Have you ever wanted to explore a lost temple? This is your chance. 
Find the treasures and escape the Temple of Aluxes by solving various puzzles and challenges.', null, null),

(61869, 'SoundSelf', 2020, 'You use your voice to explore a hypnotic world of sounds and visuals that feel like they are emerging directly from your body. Each tone will navigate you through strobing tunnels-of-light, impossible shapes, and into a meditative trance.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1xle.jpg', 23957),

(61859, 'Dark Deception', 2018, 'A first-person horror game by indie developer Glowstick Games. The player must run through a maze of corridors, collecting shards and avoiding giant knife-wielding toy monkeys, in a decidedly Pac-Man-like fashion.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2j92.jpg', 26764),

(62141, 'Space Live: Advent of the Net Idols', 2017, 'Humanity abandoned reality and decided to reside in Net Space. Net Space is divided into a number of factions, and every four years, they hold a concert for control of all the Spaces. With such high stakes at play, the heated battle between Space Idols shall commence!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co27dy.jpg', null),

(62113, 'Intruder', null, 'Intruder is a Squad-Based First-Person Stealth Shooter with deadly gunplay, interactive environments, and spatial audio.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/a7ewgxcjg0f1xjn0xptu.jpg', 18512),

(63281, 'The Unlikely Legend of Rusty Pup', 2018, 'The Unlikely Legend of Rusty Pup is a 2D platformer with a strong focus on character and a sad story seasoned with dark humor. It is developed by the creator of Conker`s Bad Fur Day and ex-RARE staffer Chris Seavor.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co27bj.jpg', 11972),

(63734, 'Elisa: Seduce the Innkeeper', 2017, 'The player doesn`t impersonate a simple man, but a powerful, rich and famous nobleman who seems to be able to obtain whatever he wishes for. But will this be enough this time?', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/lj6cyop3euu9wvzykh4e.jpg', null),

(64359, 'Hero-U: Rogue to Redemption', 2018, 'An hybrid role-playing game from the designers of Quest for Glory. This new hybridization is based around incorporating the iconic elements of King`s Quest and Quest for Glory in a new, immersive format.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co218w.jpg', 24761),

(65825, 'BattleCore Arena', 2017, 'In BattleCore Arena, you assume the role of a Core in a world ruled by physics! Jump, dash, fire, explode and eject your enemies from the arena before you suffer the same fate! 
Because we love you, we prepared 2 game modes for you, with different rules!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1klp.jpg', 19170),

(65838, 'Odysseus Kosmos and his Robot Quest', 2017, 'A classic COMEDY QUEST about being geeky and procrastinative in SPACE!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co22rs.jpg', null),

(65842, 'Accel World VS. Sword Art Online Deluxe Edition', 2017, 'Svart Alfheim and the Accelerated World have begun to merge. In the midst of the chaos, Yui has gone missing. Kirito must challenge the Seven Kings of pure color from the Accelerated World to gain access to her location. 
 
In the Americas, a limited time digital deluxe launch edition of the game will also be available. It will include two exclusive downloadable content packs. 
 
