- Knight of the Blood Oath Costume 
- Fairy Dance Avatar Costume — Kirito', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co24wf.jpg', null),

(65834, 'Game Tengoku', 2017, 'Game Tengoku CrusinMix is a vertically scrolling shooting game mixing cute characters, a game world parodying a wide range of gaming tropes and history, tight controls, refined mechanics and eggplants?!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co26xp.jpg', null),

(65795, 'Elise the Devil', 2017, '世界を支配しようと企んでいた魔王イブリースだったが、勇者に敗れて弱体化し、少女のような姿になってしまう。 
密かに復讐を誓う魔王。彼女は名をイリスと変えて、力を取り戻す旅に出る。その前に立ちはだかる、欲望に塗れた人間たちと 
反旗を翻したモンスターたち!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2cqs.jpg', 15985),

(65809, 'Crimson Sword Saga: Tactics Part I', 2017, 'Crimson Sword Saga: Tactics is a SRPG inspired by series such as Fire Emblem and Langrisser (Warsong). The storyline follows Prince Abel of Meyr as he battles the Ranasseh Empire to claim back his country.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/sfjuvntu6pvw05srqz8e.jpg', null),

(65813, 'Code World', 2017, 'Do you want to learn programming while playing video game or test your code writing skills? This puzzle game is here for you! In Code World you control the robot that can walk around the world and send messages to devices. Every device reacts on those messages according to its Python code. You will have to read this code, understand what messages to send and write your own code.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2ak1.jpg', null),

(65835, 'Field of Glory II', 2017, 'Field of Glory II is a turn-based tactical game set during the Rise of Rome from 280 BC to 25 BC. It allows you to fight large or small battles for or against Rome, or between the other nations who are as yet unaware of the Roman threat, or what-if battles between nations that never came into conflict historically.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1ymh.jpg', null),

(65786, 'After Death', 2017, 'After Death is a platform / exploration game in a dark and hostile world. With the help from lost souls, you will have to find a way to open a gate which seems to be the only exit from this mysterious world infected by monsters.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co22mw.jpg', null),

(67203, 'Indie Pogo', 2018, '"Indie Pogo is a platform brawler game for 2-4 players about bouncing, ricocheting, and pogoing your friends into oblivion! 
 
It’s sort of like if we replaced the cast of Smash Bros. with 30+ indie fighters and gave them all trampolines to fight on. 
 
Inspired by games like Super Smash Bros, Legend of the Mystical Ninja, and League of Legends, we are developing a competitive yet quirky game that is easy to learn yet difficult to master. 
 
After collaborating with over 50 studios across 15 different countries, we`re striving to create the ultimate indie crossover!"', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1td3.jpg', 13481),

(67915, 'StepX', 2017, 'The most popular music game is now available on steam. The easiest way to realize your musical ideas is with just a few mouse clicks. In front of you is a panel with notes with different musical instruments. You can adjust the tempo, volume, tonality. You can import and export your creations.', null, null),

(67929, 'Rainbow Step', 2017, 'Teru Teru Bouzu, with the mysterious ability to clear the rain, journeys though the world in this 3D adventure game. 
Why is it always raining in this magical world? 
Solve the mystery by using the mysterious ability to clear the rain while riding rainbows to explore this magical world.', null, null),

(67600, 'Marshmallow Melee', 2017, 'Marshmallow Melee is VR rogue-lite dungeon crawler with toy-sized warriors. 
 
Rally your troops and fight your way to the top of an ever-shuffling tower to defeat Steve, The Evil Wizard.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/shqefqbobeuk7xegzxp4.jpg', null),

(67904, 'Armored Kitten', 2017, 'Awesome side scroll action about Cute and Deadly Kitten with a double shotgun!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co234x.jpg', 24991),

(67598, 'Devil in the Pines', 2017, 'An Appalachian man makes a desperate final move to save his sick daughter`s life. But after unknowingly stepping onto cursed land, he now also finds himself in a fight to save his own.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2asg.jpg', null),

(67626, 'Fugl', 2017, 'Fugl is a meditative game in which you experience the thrill of flying as a bird. Feel the breeze under your wings as you glide serenely across picturesque landscapes, or kick up the excitement and soar up steep cliffs like an eagle. With no set rules the free roaming gameplay let’s you discover the unspoilt beauty and secrets of the world at your own pace. 
 
