(75005, 'aMAZE Double', 2017, 'aMAZE Double is a straightforward and surprisingly-difficult celebration of the simple beauty of the maze with portal and gem`s', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co26o9.jpg', null),

(75306, 'Space Panic Defense', 2017, 'A futuristic tower defense game with action and strategy!', null, null),

(75498, 'Operation Apex', 2017, 'A virtual reality underwater adventure for the Vive in which you, a citizen scientist, take control of a research rig in order to learn about the current state of the oceans. As you begin to learn how to study the seas you are witness to one of the largest great white sharks ever seen. Moments later, your mission is clear - travel through the kelp, down the continental shelf and out in the open ocean to find and scan the mysterious shark.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/mgyvasfrk7krebtnp2jp.jpg', null),

(75033, 'Chromalocity', null, 'Chromalocity is a First-Person Speedrunning Platform Shooter. Using your ChromaCannon and its powers, you must traverse the terrain, finding the shortcuts along the way to set the fastest times.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/irsrze9j9ljxqnbr7dzg.jpg', 15961),

(75496, 'Unforgiving - A Northern Hymn', 2017, 'All the stories being told to scare children is actually true. The Swedish folklore is real and it`s coming for you! 
This first person horror game is heavily inspired by Swedish folklore and the Nordic mythology to create the nightmares that`s been haunting Swedish children for many generations.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co24ll.jpg', null),

(75069, 'ShadowCore VR', 2017, 'ShadowCore is a HeroFps-light, virtual reality, action paced, multiplayer shooter in Sci-Fi. Focused on small to medium tactical engagements. Supporting skilled shooting in combination with easy to access gear.', null, null),

(75620, 'Puzzle Chambers', 2017, 'You wake up in a mysterious place and can’t remember how you got there. After that, you meet few other people who are in the same boat and make first contact from your seemingly mentally deranged hosts. Oh, and you also have super powers.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1p6m.jpg', null),

(75520, 'Unknightly', 2017, 'Unknightly is a medieval VR stealth game designed from the ground up for virtual reality. 
