with the plan of returning to rob the "Knight`s Order" of all of its valuable belongings!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co274a.jpg', null),

(75518, 'Nirvana Pilot Yume', 2017, 'Nirvana Pilot Yume is the cure for your ‘80s sci-fi anime nostalgia. Experience SkyRoads-inspired space races and a steamy visual novel of romance and redemption. Turn on the neon lights and raise the volume of the synthwave soundtrack: you are at home.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/rv9fgmf3nm1a2kx4wf0s.jpg', 13858),

(75778, 'Labyronia Elements', 2017, 'The five elemental worlds are in peril. Guide the protagonist "Dark One" to uncover the mysteries of the divided universe. Labyronia Elements is a JRPG delivering unprecedented, nonlinear progression, strategic battle scenes and a breathtaking story.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co274v.jpg', null),

(75606, 'No King No Kingdom', 2017, 'No King No Kingdom is a first person strategy in which you can ride on a Dragon, manage villagers, build your kingdom, raise a large army, travel to the different lands, meet different races and fantastic monsters, collect artifacts and just conquer the world!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co24zx.jpg', null),

(75636, 'Squarism', 2017, 'SQUARISM is a minimalist logic game about combining pieces scattered around into a perfect square. Complete all 70 lovely-crafted levels and become master of square assembling!', null, null),

(75913, 'NEKO-NIN exHeart +PLUS Saiha', 2017, 'From developer Whirlpool comes the 2nd mini-sequel to NEKO-NIN exHeart featuring the sub-character, Saiha! 
 
Saiha tells the protagonist, a runaway ninja has sneaked their way into town. 
