(77534, 'KovaaK 2.0', 2018, 'Trusted by thousands of players including current and former pros, KovaaK 2.0 is the definitive FPS training software. With customizable playlists, 5,500+ scenarios, guided training, performance analysis, realistic physics, and more, it’s never been easier to become a human aimbot!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2hs0.jpg', null),

