(81729, 'Leisure Suit Larry: Magna Cum Laude - Uncut and Uncensored', 2017, 'With gorgeous co-eds everywhere, college dweeb Larry Lovage is chasing around more than his diploma. He`s trying to live up to the legend of his uncle, Larry Laffer, everyone`s favourite polyester playboy. Larry Lovage is a typical college student. He lives in a dorm, has a crush on his biology professor, and goes to bars with his buddies. But when a TV dating show comes to campus, Larry gets a chance for national sexposure. If he can show that he can make any girl on campus swoon, he will become a campus legend.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2erm.jpg', null),

