(84532, 'Company of Heroes - Legacy Edition', 2006, 'Delivering a visceral WWII gaming experience, Company of Heroes redefines RTS by bringing the sacrifice of heroic soldiers, war-ravaged environments, and dynamic battlefields to life. This legacy version also grants access to the latest version of COH, just called "Company of Heroes".', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1yop.jpg', null),

