(86499, 'Zombie Solitaire 2 Chapter 3', 2018, 'Solitaire fun for the whole family! Can you save the world from the Zombie invasion? A hot lead to the ultimate Zombie hangout fills you with new hope. So get going and master exciting solitaire matches, sugar sweet Match 3 duels and lightning fast time management battles.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co23v2.jpg', null),

(86299, 'Fallen ~Makina and the City of Ruins~', 2018, 'Rumors of mystery, treasure, and adventure have been spreading across the land about the Ruins of Gardona. It has brought many travelers and adventurers to the city, including Makina, a renowned swordswoman known throughout the kingdom. However, there’s something amiss about this place… 
 
