(86430, 'Chinese Parents', 2018, '这是一款轻松休闲，且充满现实隐喻的模拟养成游戏，模拟从出生到高考这段过程，探讨中国孩子与家长之间的关系，是一款现实主义游戏。希望玩家可以分享和家长有关的趣事，我们将采纳并放入游戏中，呈现给大家。', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co23we.jpg', null),

(86395, 'SYNTHETIK: Legion Rising', 2018, 'SYNTHETIK is an unforgiving shooter rogue-lite set in a world overrun by machines. Battle from floor to floor, defeating an array of robotic forces using powerful weapons, upgrades, and quick reflexes in this gun-play focused fun-fest!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1ndd.jpg', null),

