(110714, 'Age of Fear: The Undead King GOLD', 2019, 'Age of Fear is a turn-based strategy series that marries a tabletop wargame with elements of RPG. Age of Fear: The Undead King GOLD is an extended version of the original game released seven years ago. This project aims to bring Age of Fear series into Open World theme!', null, null),

