(110737, 'The Watson-Scott Test', 2018, 'Take the Watson-Scott personality test and discover your deepest and darkest fears. 30 multiple-choice questions will tell you if you`re more afraid of clowns, snakes, or something more sinister...', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co27bo.jpg', 16808),

