(111353, 'Bugs Must Die', 2019, 'Do you want to live like a coward for a lifetime? Or live like be a hero, even if only for a few minutes? Show your bravery in Bugs Must Die!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1m91.jpg', 17939),

