(111700, 'Human Rocket Person', 2018, 'Human Rocket Person is an absurd & fun platformer where you jump & fly through different levels on your trusted pogo stick using ass-juice as fuel. It’s unbearably hard and by the end of this game, you will never play a platformer again.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1i9u.jpg', 17133),

(111882, 'Fenimore Fillmore: 3 Skulls of the Toltecs', 2019, '3 Skulls of the Toltecs was one of the last classic point & click adventure release in 1996, now you can play it again in this wonderful remastered version with enhanced graphics up to 4k.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1js3.jpg', 2982),

(111803, 'Hello, Good-bye', 2010, 'Hello, Good-bye is a Japanese adult visual novel. The primary focus of the game is the appeal of the four female main characters. The story resolves around the protagonist, Kaito Toubu, a secret agent tasked with infiltrating the demilitarised territory of Morino in an alternate universe Japan.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2oaw.jpg', null),

(111842, 'Ancient Enemy', 2020, 'An unusual, strategic RPG card game from the makers of Shadowhand and Regency Solitaire. 
 
