(112588, 'Field of Glory: Empires', 2019, 'Field of Glory: Empires is a grand strategy game in which you will have to move in an intricate and living tapestry of nations and tribes, each one with their distinctive culture. Set in Europe and in the Mediterranean Area during the Classical Age, experience what truly means to manage an Empire.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1ymi.jpg', null),

