(116271, 'Touhou Kanjuden ~ Legacy of Lunatic Kingdom', 2015, 'Touhou Kanjuden ~ Legacy of Lunatic Kingdom is the fifteenth official installment of the Touhou Project. It was announced by ZUN on his personal blog on April 22, 2015, at 20:57 JST. A playable demo was released in May 10, 2015, at Reitaisai 12.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1raz.jpg', null),

