(116544, 'Alchemy Story', 2019, 'Discover a world of magic, cute creatures and adventure in Alchemy Story, a casual farming simulation game! Grow your garden, brew potions, care for your pets and meet new friends!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1pyn.jpg', null),

(116582, 'Tidal Tribe', 2019, 'In classical god game fashion, Tidal Tribe gives you the power to shape the terrain. Raise and lower the land to protect your village from floods and waves, all while using that very same water to build lakes and rivers, turning the desert land into a lush forest of trees and bushes.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1m5k.jpg', 20582),

(116824, 'Killer Chambers', 2019, 'Killer Chambers is an action-platformer/memory-game hybrid. You must survive in small rooms filled with traps until one turn of the hourglass. Even if you`re hit only once you die! Nothing is left to chance, every trap pattern is made to be challenging yet fun to solve. The player must arm himself with quick reflexes and good (muscle) memory.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1kii.jpg', 19088),

(117032, 'Alchemia', 2018, 'Alchemia is a cryptic puzzle game which is solved through research outside of the game. 
 
