(117217, 'Chippy', 2019, 'Chippy is a twin-stick bullet-hell shooter. Chip apart destructible bosses pixel-by-pixel.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co268j.jpg', null),

(117281, 'Nightmare Reaper', 2019, 'Nightmare Reaper is a dark and violent meld of retro and modern action games, mainly inspired by the classic 2.5D first person shooters of the 90s like Doom, Duke Nukem 3D, Blood, Rise of the Triad and Wolfenstein 3D. 
 
