(117643, 'Radio General', 2020, 'It`s WW2. You`re a general sitting in a tent. All you have in front of you is a map, and a radio. Can you win the battle? Radio General is a unique strategy game where you interact with your units over the radio using speech recognition. Test your mettle and relive famous battles as a WW2 general.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2ch1.jpg', null),

(117546, 'eBall', 2019, 'eBall is an old-school multiplayer arena shooter with high speed gameplay and a minimalistic look. An old school rocket and grenade in combination with rattling speed gameplay and predictive air shoot of a classic arena FPS with the power of modern gaming technology.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1l2c.jpg', 19900),

