(118815, 'Touhou Kikeijuu ~ Wily Beast and Weakest Creature', 2019, 'Touhou Kikeijuu ~ Wily Beast and Weakest Creature (東方鬼形獣　～ Wily Beast and Weakest Creature) is the seventeenth official installment of the Touhou Project. It was announced by ZUN on his personal blog on April 17, 2019, at 14:02 JST. A playable demo was released on May 5, 2019, at Reitaisai 16. The full version was released August 12, 2019, at Comiket 96.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co268x.jpg', null),

